reviews.text: Very nice cheap eat. Some staff can speak excellent English and was very helpful in introducing the different dishes to us. Will be back.
Best wontons in my opinion. The only thing that can be improved is they use one off disposable utensils and cutlery. So I try to bring my own sometimes.
Thin wrappings wonton in szechuan spice soup.  Street food price.

I have been JunJun's no.1 fan since they opened years ago. The bosses are super friendly and consistent in their food quality. The Sichuan noodles and wontons are definitely some real deals. Considering the location is pretty close to Mongkok, I'd say the price is very affordable. Everytime I return to HK, I always pay them a visit without fail. This would be a place that people are happy to wait for the seat and food and say it's totally worth the wait. 

Love you guys. I'll come visit soon :)
Average Cold Noodles. Still delicious. Cheap though, and perfect for on the go.

result.name: 津津好好味

reviews.text: Very nice cheap eat. Some staff can speak excellent English and was very helpful in introducing the different dishes to us. Will be back.
重慶風味小雲吞，有不同辣度，每次食完都成頭大汗，爽呀!但對比在舊舖時候的味道，覺得是退步了!不過價錢不貴，仍然值得一試。

첫날 완자 들어간 면하고  잡 뭐시기 면(한자로 대충...)을 먹었는데 완자가 특히 맛있고 마라로 맛을 냈는데  그 국물도 괜찮았다  사진의 왼쪽 면도 볶은 콩과 고기 등이 들어가 국물이 살짝 달달하니 좋았다
주인아저씨가  친절하시고 영어도 잘 하셔서 주문도 편히했다 
이틀 뒤에는  냉면(?)을 사먹었는데 작은 것 12홍콩달러  간장+고추기름+약간의 고추+고수+땅콩+숙주 조합이 맛있었다  왜 이제 알았을까..... 또먹고싶다ㅠ
Best wontons in my opinion. The only thing that can be improved is they use one off disposable utensils and cutlery. So I try to bring my own sometimes.
好吃😊美味鮮
